speaker.name: Omar Sanseviero
speaker.biography: Omar Sanseviero is a Machine Learning Engineer working at Hugging Face in the Open Source team democratizing the usage of Machine Learning. Previously, Omar worked as a Software Engineer at Google in the teams of Assistant and TensorFlow Graphics. Omar is passionate about education and co-founded AI Learners, a Spanish-speaking community of people that want to learn about AI and its different applications.
